room_title: Escape room "The Asylum" by CluedIn Escape Rooms in Chicago
review: Asylum Escape RoomNice escape room experience! It was well thought out and all clues made sense, though we took a long time on some of them. Four of us worked well together to escape with 50 seconds to spare!

room_title: Escape room "The Asylum" by CluedIn Escape Rooms in Chicago
review: We did the Asylum experience and had the best time. Used this as a team bonding experience. As the manager, it made me realize even more that I have a great team (which I already knew). Looking forward to trying another room.

room_title: Escape room "The Asylum" by CluedIn Escape Rooms in Chicago
review: Wonderful escape room! We did Asylum and loved it. The puzzles are challenging without being impossible. We will definitely be back!
